1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 32=

3
00:00:53,399 --> 00:00:54,000
It's done.

4
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,119
Very well.

5
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:02,159
Can you let Churan go now?

6
00:01:04,550 --> 00:01:06,399
You can't even protect your woman.

7
00:01:06,637 --> 00:01:08,079
Are you really her husband?

8
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,799
Actually,

9
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,387
I can take care of her for you.

10
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:12,879
It's fine.

11
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,439
I don't mind second-hand goods.

12
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,359
Wu Xin,

13
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,712
how dare you?

14
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:17,920
I won't spare you.

15
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:20,439
Too bad you won't get the chance.

16
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,270
- Move.
- What are you doing?

17
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,079
What are you doing?

18
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,359
Sihai?

19
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:26,079
Mr. Ye, I failed to protect you.

20
00:01:26,290 --> 00:01:26,599
You...

21
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:27,079
Come here.

22
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:32,599
You all can leave.

23
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,879
You should've

24
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:39,280
died with your parents 20 years ago.

25
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,359
Mr. Ye.

26
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,640
Wait.

27
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,439
Do you have any last words?

28
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,840
I admit I lost.

29
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,040
But at least let me die
with some closure.

30
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,959
How did you kill my parents?

31
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,280
Enough.

32
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,280
I'll give you

33
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,937
the closure you want.

34
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,612
It's all your parents' fault
for being stupid.

35
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,959
They had a great formula.

36
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:10,760
We could've
gotten rich together with it.

37
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,787
But they just had to release it for free

38
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,360
and donate it to the country.

39
00:02:14,550 --> 00:02:15,759
They blocked my way to money.

40
00:02:16,925 --> 00:02:18,719
They deserved to die.

41
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:20,599
How did you do it?

42
00:02:20,912 --> 00:02:22,000
It's simple.

43
00:02:22,687 --> 00:02:24,439
I have money.

44
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,360
I can pay off Song Nanshan.

45
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:30,840
I can hire a lowlife driver

46
00:02:30,925 --> 00:02:33,560
and get him to drive over your parents.

47
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,599
That's it.

48
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:40,879
Alright.

49
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,360
No need to say more.

50
00:02:47,987 --> 00:02:49,198
Last question.

51
00:02:50,275 --> 00:02:51,479
I'm curious.

52
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,120
When you find out that all the effort

53
00:02:54,837 --> 00:02:56,319
and money you spent

54
00:02:56,562 --> 00:02:57,680
on getting that formula

55
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:01,120
is actually available for free online,

56
00:03:02,462 --> 00:03:04,381
will it drive you crazy?

57
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:06,800
What did you say?

58
00:03:07,425 --> 00:03:08,520
I said,

59
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,280
the formula's available for free online.

60
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,120
Dad,

61
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,960
the formula's trending now.

62
00:03:18,090 --> 00:03:19,240
It's all over the internet.

63
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:23,879
No way.

64
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:24,919
How is this possible?

65
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:25,759
How did this happen?

66
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,919
It's simple.

67
00:03:27,112 --> 00:03:29,240
My friend, Daokun,
hacked into your computer

68
00:03:29,612 --> 00:03:31,639
and posted the formula online.

69
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,700
No one can touch my computer.

70
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,475
How is it possible that it was hacked?

71
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,840
If you never turned it on
or connected to the internet,

72
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,400
I couldn't control it.

73
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:41,759
But didn't you just turn it on
and connect earlier?

74
00:03:41,837 --> 00:03:42,797
You got the password

75
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,280
and decrypted the formula.

76
00:03:44,550 --> 00:03:46,199
You thought the Song family's internet

77
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,360
was all safe, right?

78
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,800
Actually, it was a same-named router
that Daokun had set up.

79
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,240
Through the gateway,

80
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,387
he implanted a Trojan virus
into your computer.

81
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:56,520
How did you know
I was using this computer?

82
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,879
I have a friend.

83
00:03:58,237 --> 00:04:00,000
And this friend is right next to you.

84
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,039
Who?

85
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,159
Ye Chen,

86
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,000
I'm fine.

87
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,360
No way.

88
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,919
I've got Song Wanting under control.

89
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,840
There's no way she could give you intel.

90
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,360
It's simple.

91
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:15,887
I have a disciple.

92
00:04:16,875 --> 00:04:18,360
When Song Wanting couldn't reach me,

93
00:04:18,537 --> 00:04:20,118
I had my disciple contact her.

94
00:04:23,675 --> 00:04:24,875
Under the window.

95
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,040
Hello?

96
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,120
Ye Chen.

97
00:04:37,812 --> 00:04:39,093
I need your help right now.

98
00:04:41,175 --> 00:04:42,964
Song Wanting told me you had a computer.

99
00:04:43,737 --> 00:04:45,025
I guessed this computer

100
00:04:45,025 --> 00:04:46,537
must be used to decrypt the formula.

101
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,959
I played along

102
00:04:48,237 --> 00:04:49,850
and posted the formula online.

103
00:04:51,550 --> 00:04:53,669
I guess that fulfills my parents' wish.

104
00:04:54,162 --> 00:04:55,092
Wu Donghai,

105
00:04:55,275 --> 00:04:57,360
did you really think
I was negotiating with you

106
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,000
or showing weakness?

107
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:01,662
I was just distracting you.

108
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:03,199
You got the password?

109
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:03,687
(Tang Sihai)

110
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,079
So Song Wanting could unplug the router

111
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:07,400
before you turned on the computer,

112
00:05:07,425 --> 00:05:08,350
giving Wang Daokun

113
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,720
the chance to hack into it.

114
00:05:20,687 --> 00:05:21,937
(Hacker Intrusion)

115
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,399
That's useless.

116
00:05:28,837 --> 00:05:30,612
The formula's already been leaked.

117
00:05:31,212 --> 00:05:33,040
The evidence of you bribing Song Nanshan

118
00:05:33,987 --> 00:05:36,480
and hiring a truck driver
to kill my parents

119
00:05:36,687 --> 00:05:37,560
is all with me.

120
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:38,987
Wu Donghai,

121
00:05:39,312 --> 00:05:40,800
you lost this round.

122
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,600
I lost?

123
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:45,000
You're still in my hands.

124
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,412
Kill him.

125
00:05:46,462 --> 00:05:47,902
Kill him now.

126
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,839
Mr. Hong,

127
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:04,879
it's your turn.

128
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:11,279
Duan Shuiliu,

129
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,720
let's settle

130
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,720
my master's grudge today.

131
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,639
All the mistakes are mine.

132
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,442
As fellow disciples,

133
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,519
spare me.

134
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:24,800
Begging me doesn't work.

135
00:06:25,650 --> 00:06:27,439
Go tell the police.

136
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,519
Mr. Ye,

137
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,560
let's just call it even today.

138
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,240
Let us go.

139
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,839
Once we're in a safe place,

140
00:06:43,150 --> 00:06:44,240
I'll let her go.

141
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:45,920
Don't come any closer.

142
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,759
If you do, I'll kill her.

143
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:48,480
Do it.

144
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,079
Honey.

145
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:07,759
Honey.

146
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,187
You've suffered.

147
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,079
No.

148
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,487
As long as you're okay.

149
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:14,639
Everyone stop!

150
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,279
Donghai.

151
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,319
Throw the knife away.

152
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,480
Squat down.

153
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,759
Throw the knife away.

154
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,600
A true hunter

155
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,639
usually shows up as the prey.

156
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:46,040
You thought you were the hunter,

157
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,780
so you used Xiao Weiwei
to capture Churan.

158
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,600
You were wrong.

159
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,560
Since Wu Xin is targeting me,

160
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:54,199
I'll let him catch me.

161
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:56,160
Only when they catch me

162
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:58,190
will they think
they've got your weakness.

163
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,959
Then they'll get cocky.

164
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,755
When they get cocky,

165
00:08:01,987 --> 00:08:03,152
they'll drop their guard.

166
00:08:03,787 --> 00:08:05,025
That's when your plan will work.

167
00:08:05,712 --> 00:08:06,232
No way.

168
00:08:07,212 --> 00:08:07,973
I don't agree.

169
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,240
Only when they're caught

170
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,240
can we live in peace.

171
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,600
And I believe

172
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:15,720
you won't let anything happen to me.

173
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,439
Bye.

174
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:29,600
- Get in.
- Hurry up.

175
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,759
Stop right there.

176
00:08:30,812 --> 00:08:32,275
(Master)

177
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,360
Master,

178
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,920
Wu Xin took Madam away.

179
00:08:35,319 --> 00:08:36,120
Churan, wait for me.

180
00:08:44,725 --> 00:08:47,137
Trash should stay in the trash can.

181
00:08:51,425 --> 00:08:52,146
Sihai,

182
00:08:52,146 --> 00:08:53,300
where'd you get that thing?

183
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,680
You should've taken it out earlier.

184
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,399
It's not too late now.

185
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:57,960
Are you serious?

186
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,840
It's a toy gun.

187
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,200
You've learned some bad things.
Where did you get this?

188
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,675
I plan to make this a lighter for you.

189
00:09:06,837 --> 00:09:07,799
Do you like it?

190
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,320
Wu Donghai,

191
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,240
you'll admit defeat this time, right?

192
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,279
I lost?

193
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:21,100
It's not over until it's over.

194
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,159
From the very beginning,

195
00:09:25,962 --> 00:09:28,639
I never planned
to let you leave here alive.

196
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,559
I've filled this place with explosives.

197
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,519
As long as I press this button,

198
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,279
everyone will turn to dust.

199
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:43,039
We'll all die together.

200
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,559
- Don't...
- Ye Chen.

201
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,120
Dad,

202
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,039
I don't want to die.

203
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,519
I'm still here.

204
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,360
Useless thing.

205
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,480
What are you afraid of?

206
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,039
Your brother is still alive.

207
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,440
With him around,

208
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,639
the Wu family won't fall apart.

209
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,900
Now,

210
00:09:59,039 --> 00:10:00,875
do you still think you won?

211
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:04,025
I, Wu Donghai, will never lose.

212
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,960
Losing means death.

213
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,519
Since it's death,

214
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,240
I might as well
drag a few others down with me.

215
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:17,799
Run!

216
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,720
Hurry!

217
00:10:22,987 --> 00:10:25,850
(Demolition, Dangerous dog inside)

218
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,639
Dad, are you crazy?

219
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:35,190
Give it to me.

220
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:35,840
Get lost.

221
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,720
Dad, are you crazy? Dad.

222
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,162
You're crazy.

223
00:10:39,162 --> 00:10:40,360
I want to live.

224
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,639
Are you crazy?

225
00:10:41,862 --> 00:10:42,502
Dad.

226
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:47,200
Mr. Ye.

227
00:10:47,837 --> 00:10:49,025
(Demolition, Dangerous dog inside)

228
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,240
Ye Chen!

229
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,559
Chen!

230
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,559
Madam!

231
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,200
Ye Chen!

232
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,000
(Demolition, Dangerous dog inside)

233
00:11:00,112 --> 00:11:01,025
(Demolition, Dangerous dog inside)

234
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,399
You did it.

235
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,925
Your parents' spirits

236
00:11:11,087 --> 00:11:12,360
can rest in peace now.

237
00:11:15,725 --> 00:11:17,399
Mr. Tang, what are you doing? Get away.

238
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,320
Don't move.

239
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:19,879
Go home.

240
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,360
Go home.

241
00:11:27,287 --> 00:11:32,225
(In Memoriam)

242
00:11:36,175 --> 00:11:38,462
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

243
00:11:47,300 --> 00:11:50,112
(In Memoriam)

244
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:56,150
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

245
00:12:06,450 --> 00:12:08,962
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

246
00:12:22,825 --> 00:12:26,700
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

247
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,399
May I ask

248
00:12:34,559 --> 00:12:35,360
who you are?

249
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,480
Chen,

250
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,399
I finally found you. I'm your aunt.

251
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:47,919
Aunt?

252
00:12:49,475 --> 00:12:50,847
Come back home with me.

253
00:12:57,812 --> 00:12:59,912
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

254
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:09,200
We've been looking for you

255
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:11,799
all these years.

256
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,639
Sihai told me

257
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:19,919
to come pick you up.

258
00:13:21,559 --> 00:13:23,279
Do you know how happy I was?

259
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:27,159
Now that I see you safe and sound,

260
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:29,559
the worry I've had

261
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,600
is finally relieved.

262
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,919
Mr. Tang has...

263
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:45,840
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

264
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,759
Sihai.

265
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:49,480
I have to thank you

266
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:52,559
on behalf of the Ye family.

267
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:56,480
Don't worry.

268
00:13:58,159 --> 00:13:59,039
The Ye family

269
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,960
won't let anyone

270
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:03,799
bully Chen anymore.

271
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,440
Mr. Tang,

272
00:14:15,159 --> 00:14:16,480
I've finally found my family.

273
00:14:17,262 --> 00:14:18,075
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

274
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,060
You can rest in peace.

275
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,279
Come home with me.

276
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,440
Your grandpa

277
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:37,759
would love to meet your wife.

278
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:55,025
(In Memoriam,
Deep condolences for Mr. Tang Sihai)

279
00:15:43,087 --> 00:15:45,575
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

280
00:15:45,662 --> 00:15:49,415
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

281
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:51,840
You were such a good son, huh?

282
00:15:54,975 --> 00:15:56,480
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

283
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,960
He's coming home now.

284
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,787
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

285
00:16:01,012 --> 00:16:02,840
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

286
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,039
What should I do?

287
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:07,320
What can I do?

288
00:16:07,462 --> 00:16:10,512
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

289
00:16:10,625 --> 00:16:13,039
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

290
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:14,399
You'll see what I can do.

291
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:17,012
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

292
00:16:17,237 --> 00:16:20,987
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

293
00:16:20,987 --> 00:16:23,850
(To be continued)

294
00:16:23,912 --> 00:16:27,362
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

295
00:16:27,362 --> 00:16:30,037
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

296
00:16:30,037 --> 00:16:36,375
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪

297
00:16:47,025 --> 00:16:49,112
♪Oh, born to shine♪

298
00:16:49,112 --> 00:16:50,750
♪Oh, growing stronger with every fight♪

299
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,312
♪Oh, never giving in♪

300
00:16:52,362 --> 00:16:53,875
♪Oh, destined to be king♪

301
00:16:53,950 --> 00:16:55,512
♪Oh, I won't surrender♪

302
00:16:55,575 --> 00:16:57,180
♪Oh, I'll rise to the top♪

303
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,750
♪Oh, my punch strikes loud♪

304
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:01,850
♪Oh, shattering the heavens♪

305
00:17:03,087 --> 00:17:06,175
♪I'm no one's shadow♪

306
00:17:06,262 --> 00:17:09,562
♪I'm the will
that even fate can't erase♪

307
00:17:09,650 --> 00:17:12,162
♪Though my enemies wish for my fall♪

308
00:17:12,262 --> 00:17:16,100
♪I'll break through the sky,
defying all odds♪

309
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:27,620
♪Oh, oh-oh, oh-oh-oh♪

310
00:17:30,362 --> 00:17:36,180
♪I've risen from silence,
into a raging fire♪

311
00:17:36,575 --> 00:17:38,277
♪Born from humiliation, forged in bone♪

312
00:17:38,337 --> 00:17:39,662
♪The world has always known my name♪

313
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:43,287
♪They will soon
see the silhouette of a king♪
